The lineage-specific, intrinsically disordered N-terminal extension of monothiol 
glutaredoxin 1 from trypanosomes contains a regulatory region.

Sturlese M(1)(2), Manta B(3)(4)(5), Bertarello A(1), Bonilla M(3), Lelli 
M(6)(7)(8), Zambelli B(9), Grunberg K(3), Mammi S(1), Comini MA(3), Bellanda 
