HIV Status Is a Greater Determinant of Low Self-perceived Life Expectancy Than 
Cigarette Smoking in a Well-resourced Setting.

Ronit A(1), Ahlström MG(1), Knudsen AD(1), Gerstoft J(1), Nordestgaard BG(2)(3), 
Benfield T(4), Nielsen SD(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Infectious Diseases 8632, Rigshospitalet, University of 
